---
import HeroSection from "../components/HeroSection.astro";
import Testimonial from "../components/Testimonial.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import OnlineShopping from "../components/images/OnlineShopping.astro";
import Finance from "../components/images/Finance.astro";
---

<Layout title="Home">
	<HeroSection />
	<main
		class="mb-36 flex flex-col gap-24 *:flex *:flex-col *:gap-8 *:rounded-lg *:py-8 *:md:gap-16"
	>
		<section id="analytics-introduction" class="items-center">
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-18 md:w-[50%]">
				<h2 class="text-center text-4xl font-semibold">Welcome to Acme</h2>
				<p class="text-center text-xl">
					At Acme, we believe that every user interaction holds valuable insights. Our analytics
					platform enables you to uncover, understand, and refine your digital strategy. With an
					intuitive and powerful interface, our solution streamlines the process of gathering,
					analyzing, and acting on user dataâ€”empowering you to make informed decisions that propel
					your business forward.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section
			id="data-driven-testing"
			class="*:flex *:flex-col *:items-center *:justify-evenly *:gap-24 md:*:flex-row"
		>
			<div>
				<OnlineShopping class="w-[85%] max-w-2xl md:w-[50%]" />
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-12 md:w-[40%]">
					<h2 class="text-center text-4xl font-semibold">Why Experiment?</h2>
					<p class="text-xl">
						In today's dynamic digital landscape, relying on instinct alone just isn't enough. By
						embracing a culture of data-driven testing, you can: Enhance User Experience: Understand
						how real users interact with different designs and functionalities. Increase
						Conversions: Identify which variations lead to better actions and revenue. Reduce
						Uncertainty: Replace guesswork with clear, actionable data. Our step-by-step approach
						guides you from setting up your first test to full-scale optimization, ensuring that
						every decision is informed by real insights.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section
			id="case-studies"
			class="*:flex *:flex-col *:items-center *:justify-evenly *:gap-24 md:*:flex-row"
		>
			<div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-12 md:w-[40%]">
					<h2 class="text-center text-4xl font-semibold">Real Results, Real Stories.</h2>
					<p class="text-xl">
						Join a growing community of innovators who have transformed their websites into
						high-performing digital assets through analytics. Explore case studies and success
						stories that illustrate how systematic experimentation leads to measurable business
						outcomes. Whether you're a startup, a growing business, or an established enterprise,
						our platform is designed to match your pace of innovation.
					</p>
				</div>
				<Finance class="w-[85%] max-w-2xl md:w-[50%]" />
			</div>
		</section>
		<section id="industry-testimonials" class="items-center">
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-12 md:w-[50%]">
				<h2 class="text-center text-4xl font-semibold">Trusted by Industry Leaders</h2>
				<p class="text-xl">
					Leading companies rely on our analytics platform to make data-driven decisions and
					optimize their user experiences. Discover why they trust us to deliver measurable results.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-evenly gap-24">
				<Testimonial
					name="Sarah Johnson"
					position="Director of Digital Marketing"
					company="TechCorp"
				>
					"Implementing A/B testing with Acme has been transformative for our business. We've seen a
					40% increase in conversions and gained invaluable insights about our users. The platform
					is intuitive and the support team is exceptional."
				</Testimonial>
				<Testimonial name="Michael Chen" position="E-commerce Manager" company="StyleBoutique">
					"The data-driven insights we've gained have been transformative. Our cart abandonment rate
					dropped by 25% after implementing changes based on data analysis. This platform has
					revolutionized our approach to optimization."
				</Testimonial>
				<Testimonial name="Rachel Martinez" position="Product Growth Lead" company="FinanceFlow">
					"As a fintech startup, we needed to move fast while maintaining trust. This platform
					helped us test new features confidently, leading to a 52% increase in user engagement. The
					statistical rigor behind each test gives us complete confidence in our decisions."
				</Testimonial>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section
			id="get-started"
			class="items-center bg-gradient-to-tr from-indigo-100 to-indigo-300 dark:from-indigo-950 dark:to-indigo-800"
		>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-18 px-4 py-8 md:w-[50%] md:px-0">
				<h2 class="text-center text-4xl font-semibold">Get Started Today</h2>
				<p class="text-center text-xl">
					Ready to unlock the full potential of your online presence? Explore how our platform can
					help you make data-informed decisions and optimize your user experiences. Reach out for a
					demo, discover our approach, or explore our blog for insights on driving growth through
					experimentation. Your path to data-driven success begins here.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
